.TH "fcoe_update_src_mac" 9 "fcoe_update_src_mac" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
fcoe_update_src_mac \- Update the Ethernet MAC filters
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" fcoe_update_src_mac
.BI "(struct fc_lport *lport "  ","
.BI "u8 *addr "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "lport" 12
The local port to update the source MAC on
.IP "addr" 12
Unicast MAC address to add
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Remove any previously-set unicast MAC filter.
Add secondary FCoE MAC address filter for our OUI.
